column1: #### MAC Address (MAC address of the device to be added e.g. 12:34:56:78:90:ab. Mandatory for each row.)
#### Group (Group name to with the device belongs to e.g. SampleGroup. Mandatory for each row.)
#### Model (Model number of the device e.g. A7024. Mandatory for each row.)
#### Hostname (Hostname of the device e.g. master-controller. Optional.)
#### VLAN Id (Vlan id e.g. 192. Optional. Recommened VLANs per row is 8. MAX limit is 4094)
#### VLAN IP (IP address of the VLAN Interface e.g. 192.167.1.1. Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN Id.)
#### VLAN Subnet (IP subnet mask of the VLAN Interface e.g. 255.255.255.0. Mandatory for VLAN lP.)
#### VLAN Helper Addr (DHCP server relay agent of the VLAN Interface e.g. 10.1.1.1. Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### VLAN Interface Description (Description of the VLAN Interface e.g. user-vlan. Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### VLAN Interface OpState (Operstate of the VLAN Interface. Take value as UP Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### PPPoE Username (PPPoE Username of VLAN Interface e.g. ip pppoe-username <username>. Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### PPPoE Password (PPPoE Password of VLAN Interface e.g. ip pppoe-password <password>. Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### PPPoE ServiceName (PPPoE Service Name of VLAN Interface e.g. ip pppoe-service-name <svc-name>. Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### Access Port (Access Port of VLAN Interface . Optional. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### DHCP Pool Name (Name of the DHCP Pool e.g. dhcp_pool_192. Optional. Recommened DHCP Pools per row is 8.)
#### Domain Name (Domain Name for DHCP Pool e.g. vlan192.com. Optional. Prerequisite: DHCP Pool Name.)
#### DNS Server 1 2 3 4 (DNS Servers for DHCP Pool e.g. 1.1.1.1. Optional. Prerequisite: DHCP Pool Name. Recommened DNS per DHCP Pool is 4. MAX 8 per DHCP Pool)
#### DHCP Default Router 1 2 3 4 (Default Routers for DHCP Pool e.g. 1.1.1.254. Optional. Prerequisite: DHCP Pool Name. Recommened Default Routers per DHCP Pool is 4. MAX 8 per DHCP Pool)
#### DHCP Network (Network number for DHCP Pool e.g. 192.167.1.0. Optional. Prerequisite: DHCP Pool Name.)
#### DHCP Mask (Network mask for DHCP Pool e.g. 255.255.255.0. Mandatory for DHCP Network if DHCP Network Prefix is not configured.)
#### DHCP Network Prefix (Network prefix for DHCP Pool e.g. 24. Mandatory for DHCP Network if DHCP Mask is not configured.)
#### DHCP Exclude Start IP (DHCP excluded address low range e.g. 192.167.1.10. Optional. No limit of DHCP Exclude Start IP per row)
#### DHCP Exclude End IP  (DHCP excluded address high range e.g. 192.167.1.10. Optional. Prerequisite: DHCP Exclude Start IP.)
#### VRRP ID (VRRP id e.g. 2. Optional. Prerequisite: VLAN id.)
#### VRRP Priority (VRRP Priority e.g. 200. Optional. Prerequisite: VRRP ID.)
#### VRRP IP (VRRP ip address e.g. 192.168.2.2. Optional. Prerequisite: VRRP ID.)
#### BG Peer IP (BG Peer IP e.g. 192.168.2.1 . Optional. Allowed only 1 per device. Prerequisite:VLAN  Id.)
#### Controller VLAN (Vlan id e.g. 192. Optional. Allowed only 1 per device.)
#### ZS Site to Site Map Name (Crypto ipsec map name for ZScaler
#### Source FQDN (local fqdn for ZScaler
#### Number of fields that can be processed per line has a limit as mentioned in release notes. Number of lines ( number of devices) will honor the maximum device limit of the MM.
#### To configure multiple VLANs or DHCP Pools please add the new headers behind the existing headers as below
